  Te7 si3 ChiuN 
  Li2 sian-siN hit jit8 am3 to3--lai5, soa3 kap i-e5 bou2 ti7 teng-hoe2-e7 lun7 to7-li2 tui3 chhian2 chiam7-chiam7 kong2 kau3 chhim, tui3 iok-liok8 kong2 kau3 siong5-se3. Koh chiong i pun2-sin an2-chaiN2-iuN7 jip8 kau3-tng5, an2-chaiN2-iuN7 thiaN to7-li2, an2-chaiN2-iuN7 pian7-pok, an2-chaiN2-iuN7 ki5-to2, an2-chaiN2-iuN7 siu7 lang5 kam2-kek, an2-chaiN2-iuN7 hoan2-hoe2 choe7-koa3, an2-chaiN2-iuN7 ke2-piN3, an2-chaiN2-iuN7 jip8-kau3; jip8-kau3 liau2-au7 an2-chaiN2-iuN7 ka7 Ia5-sou cho3 cheng3. Hiah-e5 tai7-chi3 tak8 chan5 kong2 liau2, kau3 lou7-boe2 kong2, ¡§Na7 m7-si7 Siong7-te3 e5 toa7 in-tian2 Ia5-sou lai5 kiu3 goa2, goa2 tek-khak eng2-eng2 si2 ti7 choe7-ok e5 tiong-ng, kin-a2-jit8 bo5 koh u7 chit e5 khoan2-sit thang chit8-ke lai5 toan5-toan5-iN5.¡¨ 
  Kong2-liau2 theh8 Seng3-keng he7 ti7 toh-teng2, ka7 in bou2 kong2, ¡§Goa2 tui3 jip8-kau3 kau3 taN, tak8 cha2-am3 tek-khak tioh8 thak8 Seng3-keng chit8 nng7 chiuN, che si7 iuN2-chhi7 sim-sin5 e5 niu5-chhau2, iah8 tek-khak tioh8 gim5-si ki5-to2: kin-mi5 hian5-chhe kap kiaN2 tioh8 kap goa2 an2-ni cho3.¡¨ 
  Li2 sian-siN thak8 Seng3-keng chit8 chiuN liau2 kap i-e5 bou2-kiaN2 cho3-hoe2 gim5 Seng3 si, cho3-hoe2 kui7-teh ki5-to2. Ki5-to2 e5 oe7 tai7-liok8 si7 kong2,¡§Goa2 e5 Pe7 Siong7-te3, chhong3-cho7 thiN-te7 lang5 mih8 e5 toa7 Chu2-chaiN2, goa2 pun2 si7 toa7 choe7 e5 lang5 ham7-loh8 ti7 ban7 hang7 ok e5 tiong-kan, bo5 hoat thang ka-ti7 kiu3, tit-tioh8 ThiN-pe7 thiaN3-thang3 lin5-bin2, Ia5-sou chin2-kiu3, Seng3-sin5 kam2-hoa3; taN e7 tit thoat-li7 khou2-hai2 chhut-si2, jip8-oah8, chit e5 in-tian2 khoah-toa7 bo5-han7-liong7, kam2-sia7 be7 tit chin7. Hian7-chai7 kiu5 goa2 e5 Pe7 Siong7-te3 chiau3-kou3 kam2-hoa3 goa2 e5 bou2-kiaN2, hou7 in long2 e7 tit-tioh8 kiu3, kap goa2 cho3-hoe2 kiaN5 ThiN e5 lou7, si2-au7 cho3-hoe2 hiong2-siu7 Thian-tong5 e5 chin hok-khi3.¡¨ 
  Chiah e5 oe7 ki5-to2 liau2, chiu7 peh-khi2-lai5 khi3 khun3. Lun7-kau3 in bou2 hit mi5 siuN7 long2 be7 khun3 tit, siuN7-khi2 in ang ke2-ku7 oaN7-sin, sim-lai7 toa7-toa7 hoaN-hi2. In ang khoan2-thai7 i e5 in-cheng5 thiaN3-thang3 pi2 eng2-siong5-si5 ka-poe7 ho2, sim-lai7 toa7-toa7 siu7 kam2-kek; khoaN3 in ang gian5-gi2, tek-heng7 un-jiu5, toan-chiaN3, ho5-peng5, sim-lai7 toa7-toa7 hang5-hok8. Lun7-kau3 sou2 ka3 i e5 to7-li2 khiok u7 oh-tit beng5-pek8 e5 sou2-chai7 chhin-chhiuN7 teh kong2,¡§Siong7-te3 si7 tok8-it bu5 ji7, it-khai3 chiah e5 phou7-sat kap sin5-beng5, ang-hut8 long2-si7 peh8-chhat8 bo5 iaN2, keng3-i, pai3-i bo5 li7-ek, iu7-koh u7 choe7.¡¨ Chit ho7 e5 oe7 taN chiah thiaN-kiN3 sim-lai7 be7 bian2-tit giau5-gi5 ki5-koai3, in-ui7 i-e5 sim chat8-chat8 iau2-boe7 khui e5 ian5-kou3 chiah an2-ni, chong2--si7 teh tiu5-tu5 e5 tiong-kan, u7 chit8-ku3-oe7 e7 beng5 e7 sin3, chiu7-si7 i-e5 ang kong2 chit e5 to7-li2 e7 pian3-hoa3 i-e5 sim, hou7 i thoat-li7 hiah e5 choe7-ok. Na7 m7-si7 chin e5 to7-li2 beh thai3-e7 kau3 an2-ni? Che oe7 chin tioh8, chhin-chhiuN7 kong2,¡§Ho2 chhiu7 tek-khak kiat ho2 e5 koe2-chi2, phaiN2 chhiu7 be7 kiat ho2 e5 koe2-chi2.¡¨TaN khoaN3 in ang u7 ho2 e5 ki2-tong7 chiu7 thang chai hit e5 to7-li2 tek-khak si7 ho2 e5 to7-li2, hian7-si5 sui-jian5 bo5 sim2-mih8 beng5-pek8, au7--lai5 tek-khak e7 ti3-kau3 long2-chong2 bat. 
  Keh jit8 cha2-khi2 khi2-lai5 se-thau5, se2-bin7, chiah8-te5, tiam2-sim liau2-au7 hap8 ka chu7-chip8 khoaN3 Seng3-keng ki5-to2 kap cheng5 mi5-hng siang7. Tak8 jit8 chiau3 an2-ni liah8 cho3 tiaN7-tioh8 e5 kui-ki2. 
  Te7 gou7 ChiuN 
  Hit chit8 jit8 Li2 sian-siN khi3 tham3-thiaN i sou2 be7 hit nng7 e5 kiaN2, chiah chai cha-pou e5 i2-keng si2, siong-sim chham2-chheh, m7-na7 in-ui7 in kiaN2 lai5 pi-ai, iah8 si7 ui7-tioh8 i ka-ti7 chai7-cha2 cho3 phaiN2 ti3-kau3 an2-ni, lai5 pi-ai. Li2 sian-siN taN chai chiong5-cheng5 sou2 u7 e5 choe7-ok si7 khou2 e5 kin, sou2 siN e5 ki-hioh8 iah8 tek-khak che7-che7 e5 kan-khou2; chheh-sim hoan2-hoe2 tai7-seng e5 chho3-gou7, tok8-tok8 pek-chhiat kiu5 Siong7-te3, tai3-liam7 Ia5-sou e5 kong-lo5 lai5 sia3 i-e5 toa7-choe7, siuN2-su3 Seng3-sin5 lai5 an-ui3 i-e5 sim. 
  Li2 sian-siN tit-tioh8 hit-ho7 phaiN2 e5 siau-sit, bo5 oe7 thang kap in bou2 kong2, iu7-koh kiu5 Siong7-te3 khoan-i in bou2 e5 sim, bian2-tit hou7 in iu-bun7 khah koe3-thau5. To3--lai5 kap i-e5 bou2 oan2-choan2 lai5 kong2, i-e5 bou2 lau5-bak8-sai2 siong-sim. Li2 sian-siN eng7 che7-che7 hong-hoat khou2-khng3 i, in bou2 koh khau3 kong2,¡§Na7-si7 cha-bou2--e5 si2, cha-pou--e5 lau5 teh, iah8 iau2 e7-kham-tit. TaN ku2 bo5 an2-ni, goa2 e5 sim-tng5 kio3 goa2 chaiN2-iuN7 m7 koa3-tiau3?¡¨ 
  Li2 sian-siN chai i-e5 bou2 seng3-to7 iau2-boe7 beng5, siok8-cheng5 iau2-boe7 hoa3, chiu7 khng3 i kong2, ¡§Hian5-chhe li2 sou2 kong2 e5 oe7 bo5 sun7 thian-li2, iah8 m7-si7 chiau3 jin5-cheng5, cha-pou cha-bou2 long2 si7 pe7-bo2 e5 kut-jiok8, nia3 thang koh-iuN7 sim khoan2-thai7 i? Goa2 iau2-boe7 thiaN-kiN3 chin-li2 e5 tai7-seng, iah8 si7 tui3-tiong7 cha-pou, m7-ai3 cha-bou2, chhin-chhiuN7 siok8-gu2 teh kong2,¡¥Cha-bou2-kiaN2 si7 liau2-chiN5-hoe3, m7 chhi7 iah8 e7-tit-koe3.¡¦Goa2 iah8 peN5-peN5 u7 chit-ho7 sim, siong5-siong5 u7 chit-ho7 oe7. Tui3 bat to7-li2 liau2-au7, chiah chai lam5-li2 long2 si7 Siong7-te3 siuN2-su3, long2 si7 Ia5-sou siok8-hoe5 e5 lang5, chai7-siN thang cho3 Siong7-te3 e5 peh-siN3, si2-au7 leng5-hun5 e7-tit kui Thian-tong5, eng2-oan2 hiong2-hok, bo5 hun-piat8 cha-pou cha-bou2. Siok8-gu2 koh kong2,¡¥Bou2-kiaN2 chhin-chhiuN7 se2-kha-chui2, piaN3 hiat-kak8 koh oaN7 sin.¡¦ Chai7-cha2 goa2 iah8 an2-ni siuN7, lam7-sam2 khai-hui3 chiN5-chai5, ke-lai7 pang3-choh8-teh bo5 chiau3-kou3, chiu7-si7 chit-ho7 sim sou2 tihN8 e5. TaN chiah chai tu5-khi3 siok8-cheng5, ai3-sioh hian5-chhe khoaN3 cho3 chit8 the2, si7 in-ui7 jip8 seng3-kau3, tit-tioh8 Siong7-te3 e5 Seng3-sin5 kam2-hoa3, sun7-than3 Seng3-keng e5 ka3-si7, chiah e7 an2-ni. Siok8-gi2 iah8 bat kong2,¡¥Lam5 u7 saN e5 bou2 si7 ho2-han3, li2 u7 saN e5 ang si7 phaiN2-lang5.¡¦Che iah8 si7 tui3-tiong7 cha-pou khoaN3-khin cha-bou2, liu5-thoan5 e5 mau5-peng7. Sam hu, sam chhe long2 m7-si7 chiau3 cheng5-li2, chhin-chhiuN7 an2-ni lai5 cho3, pai7-hoai7 jin5-lun5, sit8-chai7 bo5 kiong5-chin7. Chiau3 Seng3-keng kong2,¡§Siong7-te3 chhong3-cho7 lang5 si7 it-lam5 it-li2,¡¨m7-si7 it-li2 liong2-lam5, iah8 m7-si7 it-lam5 liong2-li2. Sou2-i2 na7 jip8 seng3-kau3--e5, siong7 chi3 hong5-te3, ha7 chi3 peh-siN3, long2 si7 chit8 ang chit8 bou2. Seng3-keng koh kong2,¡§Ang tioh8 thiaN3-bou2 chhin-chhiuN7 ka-ti7, thiaN3 bou2 chiu7-si7 thiaN3 ka-ti7, lang5 m7-bat oan3-hin7 ka-ti7 e5 seng-khu--e5, long2 si7 po2-sioh i.¡¨Koh kong2, ¡§Lang5 li7-khui pe7-bo2 chhin-chhiuN7 i-e5 bou2, lai5 hap8 cho3 chit8 the2; sou2-i2 tak8 lang5 eng-kai tioh8 thiaN3 bou2 chhin-chhiuN7 ka-ti7, bou2 iah8 tioh8 thiaN3 i-e5 tiong7-hu, lai5 chun-keng3 hang5-hok8--i.¡¨Chit-ho7 oe7 kek8 che7, kong2 be7-tit chin7. 
  I-e5 bou2 thiaN-kiN3 chiah-e5 oe7, chai in ang sou2 kong2 long2 hap8 to7-li2, sou2 cho3 iah8 si7 an2-ni, sim-lai7 chiam7-chiam7 hoaN-hi2 siu7 i an-ui3, tok8-tok8 ti3-i3 teh-beh siok8-hoe5 chit-e5 cha-bou2-kiaN2. 
  Li2 sian-siN chhut-khi3 chha5 cha-bou2-kiaN2 e5 he7-loh8, chiong chiN5 siok8 to3-tng2--lai5. In bou2 khoaN3-kiN3 i-e5 cha-bou2-kiaN2 to3--lai5, sim-lai7 hoaN-hi2, lam2 lai5 pho7 ti7 heng-cheng5, ai3-sioh chhin-chhiuN7 po2-poe3, eng7 chhiu2 so in cha-bou2-kiaN2 e5 bin7 kong2, ¡§Li2 e5 bin7-mau7 chhin-chhiuN7 an2-nia5-e5.¡¨Koh khoaN3 i-e5 sin-hun7 kong2,¡§TaN pi2 hiang3-si5 khah toa7-han3 lah.¡¨Chim-chim chng7-chng7, kong2 tang mng7 sai, bo2-a2-kiaN2 kong2 be7-tit soah. Li2 sian-siN ti7 piN--a2 khoaN3 in chit-ho7 e5 khoan2-sit, hoaN-hi2 kau3 lau5 bak8-sai2, soa3 bo5 oe7 thang kong2, tok8-tok8 kong2 chit8-ku3,¡§Che si7 Siong7-te3 toa7 in-tian2 lah.¡¨ 
  Te7-lak8 ChiuN 
  Hit chit8 me5 cha-bou2 gin2-na2 kap in lau7-bo2 cho3-hoe2 khau3, kha siong5-siong5 chhun-teh kiu-teh, chhui3-lai7 teh ihN8-ihN8 ng-ng haiN-haiN-chhan. I-e5 lau7-bo2 ti7 bin5-bang7-tiong kiaN-chheN2, chiah chai i-e5 cha-bou2-kiaN2 si7 kha teh thiaN3. I bo5 hoat ta7-oa5, chong2--si7 iong7 oe7 an-ui3 i nia7-nia7. Bin5-a2-cha2-khi2 i-e5 lau7-pe7 mng7 i, in lau7-bo2 ka7 i kong2, si7 kha thiaN3. Li2 sian-siN kong2,¡§Goa2 thiaN-kiN3 cha-bou2-kiaN2 teh hiN-hiN-hau2, se3 siaN teh chhan, phah-sng3 si7 in-ui7 pak8-kha khi2-in, taN ko2-jian5 si7 an2-ni. Hai3 lah! Chin ki5-koai3! Tiong-kok pak8-kha e5 hong-siok8, tui3 Bong5-niu5 siat khi2-thau5, kau3 kin-a2-jit8 liu5-thoan5 na2 hai7, u7 lang5 pak8 kau3 nng7 saN chhun3 hiah se3. ¡¨ 
  Siok8-gi2 kong2,¡§Toa7 kha tah8 te7 un2, se3 kha ka-lun2-sun2.¡¨Chiau3 an2-ni lai5 khoaN3, pak8-kha m7-si7 ho2 hong-siok8, m7-si7 hok-khi3 e5 siong3-the2. TaN-chiah pak8 e5 si5 thang3-thiaN3 lan5 tong, me5-jit8 thi5-hau2, poaN3-pou7 be7 kiaN5 be7 soa2, phoe5-hu kha-bak8 hiu2-noa7, lau5-hoeh chhut-lang5, kap siu7 choe7 e5 hoan7-lang5 siang7 chit8-iuN7. Pe7-bo2 khoaN3 i thai2-tho2 e7 jim2-sim, bo5 beh lin5-bin2 leh, pak8 kau3 toa7-han3 phaiN2 kiaN5-tah8. Siat-su2 tu2-tioh8 bo5 tiuN-ti5 e5 chai-iong, kin2-kip e5 tai7-chi3, beh thai3 chau2 e7 li7 thang siam2-pi7, kau3 hit-tiap8 chong2--si7 si2. Hian5-chhe chhiaN2 li2 thiaN goa2 e5 oe7, koaN2-kin2 chiong i e5 kha ka7 liu5--khi2--lai5. 
  In bou2 kong2,¡§Cha-bou2 lang5 kha toa7-e5, khah choe7 si7 cho3 ha7-chian7 hou7 lang5 chhe-eng7, lang5 long2 ka7 i chhiok-ho7, kio3 cho3 toa7-kha-po5, hit-ho7 oe7 thiaN long2 be7 jip8 hi7. Goa2 khoaN3 i kan-khou2 khiok iah8 siong-sim, m7-ku2 hong-siok8 to si7 an2-ni, thai3 thang kap lang5 bo5 siang7-khoan2, kaN2-tioh8 pak8 khah ho2.¡¨ 
  Li2 sian-siN kong2,¡§Hong-siok8 u7 ho2, u7 phaiN2; na7 ho2--e5 tioh8 than3 i, na7 phaiN2--e5 chiu7 tioh8 oaN7. Pak8-kha si7 kek8 phaiN2 e5 hong-siok8, chhiat-chhiat tioh8 ke2-oaN7, koaN2-kin2 tioh8 ke2-oaN7. Kau3 au7--lai5 tek-khak thong kok long2 e7 ke2-oaN7. Chong2--si7 bo5 chit8 lang5 cho3 khi2-thau5, chiu7 bo5 ng3-bang7 e5 jit8-chi2. Na7-si7 chit8-ke tiam3 chit hiuN-li2, e7 tai7-seng ke2-oaN7, m7-bian2 hoan5-lo2 bo5 lang5 oh8 lan2 e5 khoan2-sit, chhin-chhiuN7 li2 sou2 kong2, hou7 lang5 kio3 toa7-kha-po5, thai3 u7 sim2-mih8 siong-kan? Goa2 khoaN3 toa7-kha, chiah si7 sun7-than3 Siong7-te3, chiau3-kou3 i sou2 hou7--lan2 e5 sin-the2, u7 sim2-mih8 ha7-chian7? KhoaN3 hiah-e5 se3-kha--e5 long2 si7 gek8-thiN, sou2 kiaN5 tiau5-ti5 beng2-kiong5 lai5 au2-ut kau3 chiaN5. Lun7 chin si7 toa7 kian3-siau3 e5 su7, hoan2-tng2 si7 chheng-hou cho3 sam-chhun3 e5 kim-lian5 lah, keng-e5--lah, tai7-ke ho7-lo2 ho7-so7, si7 in2-iu2 be5-hek8 lang5 e5 oe7, ka7 i pang3 cho3 bo5 thiaN-kiN3 iah8 thang.¡¨ 
  I e5 bou2 kong2, ¡§Tiong7-hu li2 sou2 kong2 e5 oe7, sit8-chai7 u7 cheng5-li2, goa2 hin7 be7-tit ka-ti7 liu5--khi2-lai5, lai5 than3 li2 e5 i3-su3, chong2--si7 chit-e5 cha-bou2 gin2-na2 na7 m7 ka7 i pak8-kha, kau3 chiong-lai5 phoe3-chhin khoaN3 beh an2-chaiN2-iuN7?¡¨ 
  Li2 sian-siN kong2,¡§Che su7 si7 Siong7-te3 chu2-i3 sou2 tiaN7 lan2 put-ko3 than3 i e5 beng7-leng7 chiu7-si7, nia3 thang in-ui7 phoe3-chhin e5 ian5-kou3 lai5 pai7-hoai7 sin-the2? Iu7-koh hit-e5 cha-bou2 gin2-na2 au7--lai5 tek-khak ka7 i phoe3 hou7 kau3-hoe7-lai7 e5 lang5, koat-toan3 m7-thang ke3-chhut kau3-hoe7-goa7; sit8-chai7 than3 to7-li2 e5 lang5 bo5 liah8 kha toa7 cho3 kian3-siau3.¡¨ 
  I e5 bou2 kong2,¡§An-chaiN2-iuN7 m7 kap kau3-hoe7-goa7 kiat chhin?¡¨ 
  Li2 sian-siN kong2,¡§Kau3-hoe7-goa7 e5 lang5 bo5 beh keng3 Siong7-te3, than3 se3-siok8, pai3 ke2 sin5, heng5-tong7 ki2-chi2 long2 li7-khui chin to7-li2, na7 chiong kiaN2 ke3 hou7 i, chhin-chhiuN7 jip8 ou-am3 e5 sou2-chai7, chai7-siN be7 sun7 Siong7-te3 e5 beng7-leng7 lai5 cho3 lang5, koe3-ong2 be7 hiong2 Thian-tong5 e5 eng2-hok. Goa2 m7 jim2 khoaN3 i pak8-kha e5 kan-khou2, thai2-tho2 e7 jim2--tit pang3 i khi3 siu7 te7-gek8 e5 kan-khou2 leh? Se3-siok8 tiong7 hu3-kui3, bo5 tiong7 to7-li2; tiong7 seng-khu, bo5 tiong7 leng5-hun5, chhian2-kian3 iu7-koh su-phian. Goa2 chai7-cha2 ia7 si7 an2-ni, taN chiah chai leng5-hun5 si7 bo5 tang3 be2 e5 po2-poe3, lang5 e5 seng-khu ban7-ban7 be7 pi2-tit. Se3-kan e5 hok-khi3 chhin-chhiuN7 poe e5 hun5, chhin-chhiuN7 gan2-chian5 hoa. Na7-si7 in-ui7 che lai5 sit-loh8 leng5-hun5, si7 ou-am3 gu5-gong7 kau3-kek8. Hai3 ah! Chin kho2-sioh! Chit-e5 cha-bou2 gin2-na2 chiu7-si7 chiong-si3-lang5 bo5 phit-phoe3, ia7 m7-kheng2 ke3 hou7 kau3-hoe7-goa7.¡¨ 
  I e5 bou2 tak8 jit8 teh siu7 i ka3-si7, sim-lai7 lioh8-a2 beng5-pek8, sou2-i2 chit-tiap8 thiaN i che7-che7 oe7, khah khoai3 e7-hiau2-tit, tui3 i-e5 tiong7-hu tim3-thau5 kong2,¡§Sian-siN e5 oe7 chin tioh8, goa2 taN kam-goan7 thau2-pang3 chit-e5 gin2-na2 e5 kha, bo5 beh koh ka7 i pak8.¡¨ 
  Chiu7 soa3 ka7 i liu5--khi2--lai5. Cha-bou2 gin2-na2 ia7 toa7 hoaN-hi2, tui3 chit-tiap8 sin-the2 chhun-un5, sim-koaN an-jian5, pi2 pak8-kha e5 cha-bou2 gin2-na2 put-chi2 khah song2-khoai3 lah. 
